name: CoreAPI Development_MediaLibrary
description: API to access Planet9 Media Library API Details
about:
Description

Planet 9-Media Library maintains the list of the media files and libraries of Planet 9. Media files consumed by Planet 9 applications.

API Development_MediaLibrary facilitates to perform the REST operations on Planet 9 Media files. You can use this API to add a file, add a folder, delete and update the media content. 

Every app must have the right roles (permissions) and authentication that enables access to the Media Library API.

Operations Performed

Get

Get the selected media library item

RequestID
ResponseMediaList(object)- Definition    


List

Get the list of the media library files and groups

ResponseMediaList(array)- Definition                  

FolderSave

Save the media folder

RequestFolderSave- Definition


FolderDelete

Delete the media folder

RequestID
